title: COINMAC SECURITY
text: COINMAC Security Services offer a full range of electronic security services including design, installation, training, consulting and support services. The range covers Video Surveillance, Biometrics, Electronic Access Control, Parking Controls, Intruder Alarm and a host range of electronic security solutions.
